Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,River of Retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RIVER OF RETRIBUTION
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rhino Cycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:17.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RHINO CYCLE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamatsu-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Are you running away again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Give me back my Shusui!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard's wounded but not giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if I follow these blood stains...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my sword now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Its Name is Enma!\NOden's Great Swords!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai went after the giant warrior-monk...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who that warrior-monk is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Kawamatsu,\NI am so glad that you are alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so grateful that you care about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Kaido... He is still tenaciously hunting for\Nthe remnants!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been beaten...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fill him with bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kappa Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorikiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kawamatsu!\N--Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamatsu... Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More enemies may be on the way.\NLet's get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on! It is hard to walk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I am no child, Kawamatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well adults do not get all pouty like blowfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. How could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe\Nthat I get to walk with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is so much I want to talk to you about,\Nbut first, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you disappeared,\NI made my way here on mundane business...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as with the neighboring Hakumai,\Nthis northern region of Ringo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:38.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,RINGO\NHAKUMAI
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was governed by the Shimotsuki Clan,\Nthat was famous for their toughness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Daimyo's name was Shimotsuki Ushimaru-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a master swordsman\Nwho was always seen in the company of a fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fox?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, just like other regions,\NRingo was destroyed by Kaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, do you know\NRingo's tradition of Eternal Graves?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I heard corpses are placed in caskets\Nand they don't decompose for centuries due to the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.\NAnd grave markers are supposed to be swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People in Ringo are given swords\Nwhen they are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will grow up with them\Nand keep them into old age.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.95,0:06:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they die, the swords they carried\Nbecome their grave markers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people are with their swords for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why those graves are called\Nthe Eternal Graves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since some of them are known as great swords,\Ngraverobbing is a continual problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is how this region, Ringo, is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you what happened\Nwhen I came here 13 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was determined that if I cut my belly,\NI would do it in this region...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, please be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Is it a monster?!\NHow creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get the weapons next time! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the curse of the samurai from Ringo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying!\NWhy can't they let me die in peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have met you once before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Onimaru, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The name of that Koma Fox was Onimaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was a companion of Shimotsuki Ushimaru-{\i0}sama{\i1},\Nthe late Daimyo of Ringo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been protecting this all by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For more than five years\Nsince Ringo was destroyed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:32.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Onimaru had been fighting by himself against grave robbers who came to steal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,weapons from the Eternal Graves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. You do not have to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is your food!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxes like fried tofu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?\NIf you do not eat, that wound will not heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you die,\Nyou cannot guard your master's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a stomachache.\NI think I ate too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It does not matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onimaru! Do not make a scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me! I know what you want to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I explain it to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not want to disturb the sleep of the dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I must do this now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0}, it's dangerous here!\NLet's get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toki-{\i1}sama{\i0}! We will protect you\Nas long as we breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave... to the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can never go back to the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can go forward into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13 years from now,\Nthere will be a big battle again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! I am sure that there will be a day\Nwhen samurai across the country stand up in high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens,\Nwe will definitely need tons of swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the battlefield, we will pick up the swords of\Nour comrades who die in front of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spirits living in those swords will make samurai stronger\Nand better able to defeat enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is still a battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Onimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle between the Animal Kingdom Pirates\Nand the Land of Wano is not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is still too early to lay these swords to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until that day comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we cannot let those robbers have the swords!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, I will collect all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hide them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is the only role...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that I have been given!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not protect Hiyori-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.11,0:14:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is the least I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to keep myself busy with something\Nor remorse will torment and kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bite off this arm already and take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stop robbing tombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:01.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIMOTSUKI USHIMARU
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you understand what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Onimaru! I will join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thus, Onimaru and I\Njoined forces to protect the graves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.15,0:15:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and collect the swords.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Another day to rob the graves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.95,0:16:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is freezing today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it goes on like this,\Nwe will have no place to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dig a hole to hide them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I sell one or two of those swords in the capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will earn money\Nto buy enough food for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.40,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An army marches on its stomach....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is for the greater good! Forgive me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am back, Onimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got some food!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is your favorite, fried tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a money-making opportunity\Nin a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingoh, are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked up on it.\NThe Eternal Graves are a treasure-trove!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can steal as many swords as we like. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Across that bridge is the main part of Ringo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave, you robbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.47,0:17:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lowlifes like you cannot have any sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Screw you! Let's do it, Bungoh, Bongoh!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to know my name?\NLet's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bandit's Bridge's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gyukimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, leave your weapons and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyukimaru?! Is it a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That warrior-monk has the same name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a short time later, I went to the capital\Nto get food,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for a certain reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was not able to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:01.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,FRIED-TOFU
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}People of the capital, I am sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're under arrest!\N--You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We caught him! You fried-tofu robber!\NStop resisting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the gravest blunder of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Onimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were held captive\Nfor 13 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a complete failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you came here to see that fox today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.12,0:19:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I am sure that Onimaru must have given up on me\Nsince I never returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been 13 years already...\NI do not think he is still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that warrior-monk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.59,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He opened this door and disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He opened the door?\NThis place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not tell me that is the path to the underground space\Nthat we created...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Is that Kin'emon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kawamatsu!\NI am glad that you are alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a lot to catch up on,\Nbut I need to tell you something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You know that we conquered Udon, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I has told by Raizo that thanks to Luffytaro-{\i1}dono{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the number of soldiers on our side was increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet you do not have enough swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly right!\NWe have been contemplating what to do about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has been taking away people's swords\Nall across the country for the last 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do not worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get thousands of soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can provide as many swords as you need!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! Truly?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send some people\Nto the location I am about to share with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right! I will do so immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.89,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onimaru did this?\NBut only humans can do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawamatsu-{\i1}sama{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fulfilled... my duty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like there are enough weapons for the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.41,0:22:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what's left to do is\Nto take back my Shusui...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.42,0:22:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorojuro-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.11,0:22:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your sword is the real Shusui,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,give it back to the Land of Wano!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.20,0:22:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you! That's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you a replacement!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.08,0:22:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword that was handed down to me\Nfrom my late father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.84,0:22:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma the famed blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.68,0:22:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a legendary sword\Nand the only weapon that ever injured Kaido!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The blade that cut Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enma...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the battle of the Emperors,\NKaido and Big Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While it rages to unexpected levels,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.22,0:23:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apoo of the Worst Generation and the Numbers,\Na group of giant creatures, arrive in Wano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another strong one joins Kaido's invincible army,\Nputting Luffy and his clan in a tighter spot!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"A New Alliance?! Kaido's Army Gathers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.57,0:23:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:48.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,